{"tid":590112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子做運動暈倒失救 途人發現送院後不治","createTime":"2018-03-12T10:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T11:33:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a458a1f962d4020b971ea8eefcf073cdcddbaa","tid":590112,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180312/57937322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57937322&d=e8AIYqEYA8e7aK928IT0H%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=54516f46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180312%2F57937322&h=4195afe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180312/57937322</a><br />\n筲箕灣配水庫遊樂場，下午2時許，警方接獲一名37歲姓梁女途人報案，稱行經上址時發現一名52歲姓柯男子身穿一身運動服，暈倒地上失去反應，救護員隨即乘車到場為事主急救，並送往東區醫院救治，最終證實不治。警方其後聯絡家屬到場確認死者身份，經調查獲悉他有身體病，初步不排除他在遊樂場運動期間突然病發昏迷，最終失救致死，事件無可疑。"},{"pid":"b0712e5b24f8eb13ea07f528644239e988418549","tid":590112,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"身體病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}